iraling (even though, yes, I did recently rewatch </mark><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">The Nightmare Before Christmas</mark></em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\"> and that absolutely contributed).</mark></p><p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"yQV2Ff6pPEIW5lTpOCXL-.webp","creator":"Crims0n_H0ll0w","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🔮 Magical","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":41,"messages":261,"created_at":"2025-12-29T10:07:09.269452+00:00"}